Privacy Policy for Weather Guide GPT Action

Thank you for using the Weather Guide GPT Action. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled in a safe and responsible manner. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information when you use the Weather Guide GPT Action.

1. Information We Collect
   When you use the Weather Guide GPT Action, we do not collect any personal information from you. The action processes your requests in real-time to provide weather-related information, but no data is stored or shared.

2. How We Use Information
   Since we do not collect personal information, there is no personal data usage involved. The Weather Guide GPT Action only processes the input you provide for the purpose of generating weather forecasts or related information and does not retain any information afterward.

3. Sharing Information
   As we do not collect or store any personal data, we do not share any information with third parties.

4. Security
   We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your data. Since no personal data is collected or stored, there are no security risks associated with your personal information when using this action.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
   We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted here with an updated effective date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your information.

